      "short": "",
      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>Your mind is a fortress. When others intrude, you can push them back with incredible force.</p>\n<p><strong>Prerequisites:</strong> @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.feats.Item.d7o4eg6e0xgstNfQ]{Iron Will}, @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.universal-creature-rules.Item.C36IM0fwUJaJPTCm]{telepathy} or @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.racial-features.Item.QmSOsPFazgFH1kKu]{limited telepathy}</p><hr /><p><strong>Benefit:</strong> When you succeed on a Will saving throw against a mind-affecting effect, you can spend 1 Resolve Point to mentally counter your foe’s attack. If you do, the source of the triggering Will save suffers a mental backlash, taking a –2 penalty to Will saves and reducing the DC of any of its spells or abilities that allow a Will save by 2 for 1 minute.</p>\n<p>@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.effects.Item.aNqfQbHgDvnXjqEX]{Effect: Fortified Mind}</p>"
